The paper discusses a machine learning method (reinforcement learning) and proposes a new potential-based reward shaping method to improve the learning speed of the agent. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The proposed method is evaluated in the Arcade learning environment, which involves robotics and control (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses transfer learning, which is a subfield of neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG and cs.AI, followed by cs.RO, cs.SY, and cs.NE.
